LICENSE AND TERMS OF USE - VINHADINHO PROJECT
1. OWNERSHIP AND COPYRIGHT
This software and all its components—including, but not limited to, source code, visual arts, characters, storylines, dialogues, and sound assets—are the exclusive property of Versão Deluxe. All rights reserved.

2. ACCESS AND CONTRIBUTIONS
The source code is made publicly available for viewing, educational purposes, and community contribution.

Contributions: By submitting improvements or bug fixes (via Pull Requests), the contributor acknowledges that the submitted code becomes part of the official project under the ownership of Versão Deluxe.

Mods: Users are permitted to create "Mods" (modifications) or new game modes, provided they function strictly as add-ons to the original game.

3. MONETIZATION AND COMMERCIAL USE

Mod Monetization: Mod creators are permitted to monetize their own original work (e.g., through donations, sponsorships, or content creation on platforms like YouTube/Twitch), provided such monetization is associated with the use of the original game.

Prohibition of External Use: It is strictly prohibited to use any characters, story elements, or code from this project to create independent (standalone) products, derivative games, or any form of commercial profit outside of the official Versão Deluxe production and distribution environment.

Asset Sale: The isolated sale of any file, artwork, or part of the source code contained in this repository is strictly forbidden.

4. NO WARRANTY
The software is provided "as is", without warranty of any kind, express or implied. Versão Deluxe shall not be held liable for any damages arising from the use of third-party modifications.

